sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(149, 165, 166) External ETL
        participant ERP as Plentymarkets ERP
        participant Talend as Talend (ETL)
    end
    box rgb(41, 128, 185) Spryker Backend
        participant Glue as Glue Backend API
        participant Import as DeltaImportProcessor + Batch Writers
        participant DB as MariaDB
        participant RMQ as RabbitMQ
    end
    box rgb(39, 174, 96) Publish & Sync
        participant Jenkins as Zed - P&S Workers
        participant Storage as Redis / OpenSearch
    end

    Note over ERP,Talend: Every 10 min, ~50 changed products (delta only)
    ERP->>Talend: Provide changed products/prices/stock
    Talend->>Glue: POST/PATCH delta batch<br/>[Glue Backend API, auth token/OAuth]
    Glue->>Import: Hand off batch
    Note over Import: Batch, not per-row; CTE bulk writes;<br/>lookups preloaded (Data Import optimization)
    Import->>DB: Bulk upsert product/price/stock
    Import->>RMQ: Trigger entity events (bulk)
    Glue-->>Talend: 2xx + accepted count (idempotent by delta cursor)

    RMQ->>Jenkins: Consume event messages (chunks)
    Jenkins->>DB: Write storage/search tables (bulk)
    Jenkins->>RMQ: Trigger sync messages
    RMQ->>Jenkins: Consume sync messages
    Jenkins->>Storage: Deliver product/price data to Redis + OpenSearch
    Note over Storage: Category PLPs now reflect delta;<br/>full-text search served by SiteSearch360 (separate feed)
